<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pending Approval - Janvi Sender App</title>
  
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; 
      display: flex; 
      flex-direction: column; 
      justify-content: center; 
      align-items: center; 
      min-height: 100vh; 
      background-color: #f0f2f5; 
      margin: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Branding Header */
    .brand-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .logo-img {
      height: 60px; 
      width: auto;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .brand-title {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1e3a8a; 
      margin-top: 5px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    /* Status Box */
    .status-box { 
      background: #fff; 
      border-radius: 12px; 
      padding: 40px; 
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 480px; 
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); 
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 6px solid #f59e0b; /* Yellow warning top border */
    }

    h1 { 
      color: #b45309; /* Darker yellow/orange for readability */
      font-size: 1.6em;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    p { 
      color: #475569; 
      font-size: 1.05em; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    strong { color: #1e293b; }

    /* Action Button */
    .btn-return {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 25px;
      background-color: #f0f9ff;
      color: #0284c7;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-return:hover {
      background-color: #e0f2fe;
      color: #0369a1;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 0.85em;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  
  <div class="brand-header">
      <img src="https://www.janvipackaging.online/images/Janvi-Packaging-Logo" alt="Janvi Packaging Logo" class="logo-img">
      <div class="brand-title">Janvi Sender App</div>
  </div>

  <div class="status-box">
    <h1>Account Pending Approval</h1>
    
    <div style="font-size: 3em; margin-bottom: 15px;">‚è≥</div>
    
    <p>Thank you for submitting your account request.</p>
    <p>For security reasons, your request requires manual review and approval by the <strong>Super-Admin</strong>.</p>
    <p>You will be able to log in immediately once your status has been updated in the system.</p>
    
    <a href="/users/login" class="btn-return">&larr; Return to Login Page</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Janvi Packaging App. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>